<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Welcome Email</title>
<style>
/* Reset CSS */
body, p, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, table, td {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
}

.logo {
    text-align: center;
}

.logo img {
    max-width: 150px;
}

.welcome-message {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.account-details {
    margin-top: 30px;
}

.account-details table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
}

.account-details td {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 10px;
}

.footer {
    margin-top: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #888;
    font-size: 14px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="https://forexon.net/images/logo.png" alt="Company Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="welcome-message">
        <h1>{{title}}!</h1>
        <p>{{message}}.</p>
        
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@forexon.net">contact us</a>.</p>
        <p>You're receiving this email because you signed up for Eliteforte service.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>